      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Fair Credit Reporting Act to prohibit the use of consumer reports and consumer information in making any determination involving personal lines of insurance with respect to a consumer, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
